{
 "name": "RPlog_Party_at_the_Manor",
 "title": "Party at the Manor",
 "summary": "Lord Geophreigh Smitherbodkins hosts a glittering, weapons-free gala at Kartathia Manor in Coronet City on Corellia, his butler J'Eeves and burly guards processing a stream of costumed guests into the chandelier-lit ballroom. Among the arrivals are the Jedi Ai'kani and her companion Silvin, the reformed deserter Jarek, Johanna, and an array of dignitaries and oddities. The festivities are shattered when an attack erupts -- a grenade hurled into the crowd is frozen mid-air and disposed of by Johanna's Force power as Ai'kani tackles the panicked Jarek clear and the cloaked Tyy'sun intervenes. The dramatic 'dud' grenade turns the elegant party into a scene of sudden, barely-averted violence.",
